    <release date="2024-12-15" version="47.1">
      <description>
        <p>
          This is the second stable release in the GNOME 47 series, with the
          following fixes since 47.0:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Fixed the problem of the "Cancel" button no longer working in
            certain cases (for example when editing a contact)
          </li>
          <li>
